data.title: Top 50 movies since the year 2000!
data.meta_description:
My personal Top 50 since the turn of the century!  I am a male in my late-40's...I like, for the most part, adult-themed, R-rated movies...these movies are most certainly not for kids! The top 34 I have given a rare 10 rating. (I will keep this list updated).

Honorable Mention, no particular order: The Grand Budapest Hotel (2014); Tape (2001); Timecrimes (2007); Hot Fuzz (2007); Big Fish (2003); Coherence (2013); The Cell (2000); Planet Terror (2007); Sin City (2005); 21 Grams (2003); Edge of Tomorrow (2014); The Pianist (2002); The Village (2004); Blow (2001); Gravity (2013); Saw (2004); Zodiac (2007); The Rundown (2003); Arrival (2016); Road to Perdition (2002); The Fog of War (2003); Mad Max Fury Road (2015); The Prestige (2006); Blade Runner 2049 (2017); Coffee and Cigarettes (2003); Isle of Dogs (2018); Dogville (2003); About Schmidt (2002); Solaris (2002); 12 Years a Slave (2013); 127 Hours (2010); Sideways (2004); Sunshine (2007); Parasite (2019); Dunkirk (2017); La La Land (2016); Antichrist (2009); Climax (2018); Whiplash (2014); Side Effects (2013); The Art of Self-Defense (2019); The Assassination of Jesse James (2007); The Bikeriders (2024)
